paragraphs.text:
%flink

val lines = benv.readCsvFile[(Long, String, String)]("/zeppelin/datasets/movies.csv", ignoreFirstLine = true, fieldDelimiter = ",")

val horror = lines.map( line => {
    val genres = line._3.split("\\|")
    (line._1, line._2, genres)
})
.filter(movie => movie._3.contains("Horror"))
.print()
